\c 8
\s Jesu unoporesa munhu unamaperembudzi
\p
\v 1 Wakati aburuka mugomo, chaunga chikuru chikamutevera.
\v 2 Zvino tarira kwakauya munhu unamaperembudzi, akamugombedzera achiti: Ishe, kana muchida, munogona kundinatsa.
\v 3 Jesu akatandavadza ruvoko rwake, akamubata, achiti: Ndinoda, chinatswa. Pakarepo maperembudzi ake akanatswa.
\v 4 Zvino Jesu akati kwaari: Vona kuti usaudza munhu asi enda unozviratidza kumupristi, ubayire chipo chakarairwa naMozisi chive chapupu kwavari.
\s Jesu unoporesa muranda womukuru wezana
\p
\v 5 Zvino Jesu wakati apinda Kapenaume, kwakauya kwaari mumwe mukuru wezana, achimukumbirisa,
\v 6 achiti: Ishe, muranda wangu uvete kumba, murwere wakafa mutezo, unotambudzika kwazvo.
\v 7 Zvino Jesu akati kwaari: Ndichauya ndizomuporesa.
\v 8 Mukuru wezana akapindura akati: Ishe, handina kufanira kuti mupinde pasi pedenga \add remba\add* yangu; asi taurai henyu shoko chete, zvino muranda wangu uchapora.
\v 9 Nokuti nenivo ndiri pasi pemasimba, ndina mauto pasi pangu; zvino ndinoti kune uyu: Enda, unoenda, nokunomumwe: Uya, unouya. nokumuranda wangu: Ita chichi, unoita.
\v 10 Jesu wakati achinzwa \add izvozvo,\add* akashamiswa, akati kuna vai\add mu\add*tevera: Zvirokwazvo ndinoti kwamuri: Handina kumbowana kutenda kukuru kwakadai kunyangwe napakati paIsraeri.
\v 11 Zvino ndinoti kwamuri: Vazhinji vachauya vachibva kumabvazuva nokumavirira, vachagara naAbhurahamu naIsaka naJakobho, muushe hwokudenga,
\v 12 asi vanakomana voushe vachakandirwa kurima rokunze; ipo pachava nokuchema nokugeda-geda kwameno.
\v 13 Zvino Jesu akati kumukuru wezana, enda, uitirwe sezvawakatenda. Muranda wake akapora nenguva iyo.
\s Jesu anoporesa mbuyawasha vaPetro
\p
\v 14 Jesu, wakati apinda mumba maPetro, akavona mbuyawasha vake vavete vane fivhiri.
\v 15 Akabata ruvoko rwavo, fivhiri ikabva kwavari: vakasimuka vakavashandira.
\p
\v 16 Akati ava madekwana vakauya kwaari navazhinji vaiva vakabatwa nemweya yakaipa; akabudisa mweya neshoko, akaporesa vose vairwara;
\v 17 kuti zvizadzisike zvakarehwa naIsaya muporofita achiti: Iye wakatora utera \add hwedu\add*, akatakura urwere hwedu.
\s Kutevera Jesu
\p
\v 18 Jesu wakati achivona chaunga chikuru chakamukomba, akaraira kuti vabve vaende mhiri.
\v 19 Zvino mumwe munyori akauya akati kwaari: Mudzidzisi ndichakuteverai kose kwamunoenda.
\v 20 Zvino Jesu akati kwaari: Mhungubwe dzine mwena, neshiri dzokudenga matendere; asi Mwanakomana womunhu haana paangatsamhidza musoro.
\v 21 Mumwe wavadzidzi vake akati kwaari: Ishe, ndiregei nditange ndambonoviga baba vangu.
\v 22 Asi Jesu wakati kwaari: Nditevere, urege vakafa vavige vakafa vavo.
\s Jesu unonyaradza dutu remhepo
\p
\v 23 Wakati apinda muchikepe, vadzidzi vake vakamutevera.
\v 24 Zvino tarira dutu guru remhepo rakamuka mugungwa, zvokuti igwa rakanga rofukidzwa namafungu. Asi Iye wakanga avete.
\v 25 Zvino vadzidzi vake vakauya, vakamumutsa, vachiti: Ishe tiponesei toparara!
\v 26 Zvino Akati kwavari: Munotyireiko, imwi vokutenda kushoma? Zvino akamuka, akaraira mitutu negungwa; Kudzikama kukuru kukavapo.
\v 27 Vanhu vakashamiswa vachiti: Uyu munhu rudzii anoti kunyange nemitutu negungwa zvinomuteerera?
\s Jesu unobudisa mweya yakaipa panyika yavaGerigesi
\p
\v 28 Wakati asvika mhiri kunyika yavaGerigesi, akasangana navaviri vaiva nemweya yakaipa, vachibuda kumarinda, vane hasha kwazvo-kwazvo zvokuti kwakanga kusina munhu wagona kupfuura nenzira iyo.
\v 29 Zvino tarira vakadanidzira vachiti: Tineiko nemwi, Jesu, Mwanakomana waMwari? Mauya pano kuzotitambudza nguva isati yasvika here?
\v 30 Zvino kure navo kwakanga kune boka guru renguruve dzichifura.
\v 31 Mweya yakaipa ikamukumbirisa ichiti: Kana muchitibudisa, titenderei kuti tiende tinopinda muboka renguruve.
\v 32 Zvino akati kwairi: Endai. Zvino yakati yabuda, ikapinda muboka renguruve; zvino tarira boka rose rakamhanyira kwazvo kumateru kugungwa, rikapararira mumvura.
\v 33 Zvino vaidzifudza vakatiza, vakaenda kuguta, vakataura zvose nezvakaitirwa vakanga vane mweya yakaipa.
\v 34 Zvino tarira, guta rose rakabuda kundosangana naJesu; vakati vamuvona, vakakumbira zvikuru kwaari kuti abve pamiganhu yavo.
